1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 10=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,360
I thought you'd forgotten

18
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,800
that you're trying to make something
out of thin air.

19
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:24,200
Well, you've got a point there.

20
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,200
But wasn't it you who proposed

21
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,720
this fifty-fifty split
in the first place?

22
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:28,840
Are you sure?

23
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:33,400
(Li Yunhe, if you can succeed,)

24
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,680
(the Marquis House)

25
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,400
(will sustain)

26
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,440
(irreparable financial damage)

27
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,680
(because of your move.)

28
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,480
(During this period,)

29
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,800
(public suspicion will rise,)

30
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:41,680
(and people will judge.)

31
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,440
(Do you think you can handle that?)

32
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,200
(Sometimes,)

33
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,240
(heroes)

34
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:50,600
(have to bear
certain misunderstandings.)

35
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:54,880
(My lord,)

36
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,600
(this man is willing to bear infamy)

37
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,040
(for common people's sake.)

38
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,520
(He's indeed a hero.)

39
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,400
(Li Yunhe!)

40
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,920
(If we can make it happen,)

41
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,600
(I am willing to)

42
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,000
(swear brotherhood with you.)

43
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,280
(Yunzhuo,)

44
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,960
(it's meaningless to talk brotherhood.)

45
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:12,000
(Let's forget about that.)

46
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,400
(If we can make it,)

47
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,520
(we'll split)

48
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,000
(the profits fifty-fifty.)

49
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,920
Yeah, that was my idea.

50
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,120
But you didn't refuse, did you?

51
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,800
By talking,

52
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,240
you want half of the profit?

53
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,520
When has anything

54
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,680
been that easy in this world?

55
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,160
40 percent then.

56
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,800
That's not too much to ask.

57
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,240
20 percent.

58
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,680
Take it or leave it.

59
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,000
Zhuo,

60
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,320
30 percent.

61
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,400
Come on.

62
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,080
That's my bottom line.

63
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,520
I really need the money.

64
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,400
Are you really not going to think about

65
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,200
the sworn brother thing?

66
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,480
Enough of that nonsense.

67
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,320
Even brothers keep the books clean.

68
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,640
No empty talk.

69
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,800
But I promise you.

70
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,400
If there's such a chance next time,

71
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,720
I'll count you in.

72
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:05,680
Li Yunhe, do you even realize

73
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,400
what you just missed?

74
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,800
You can't even imagine.

75
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,400
What could I possibly miss?

76
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,240
Even if I become his sworn brother,

77
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:11,880
it's not like

78
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,720
he'd make me a lord

79
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,280
or part of the royal family.

80
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,720
It's none of your business.

81
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,600
Sit down.

82
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,600
I...

83
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,640
Zhuo.

84
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,120
Kid, stay out

85
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,040
of adults' business.

86
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,800
So, Zhuo, about the money,

87
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,400
will you give me cash or notes?

88
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,720
Take it easy.

89
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:32,000
I'll keep my word.

90
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,000
But not now.

91
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,440
Zhuo,

92
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,000
I've been sincere with you.

93
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,280
And you're tricking me instead?

94
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:44,880
20 percent.

95
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,400
Is that okay?

96
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,200
Nope.

97
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,600
10 percent then.

98
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,400
That's all I ask.

99
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,600
It's not that I won't give you.

100
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:54,640
I just have other plans

101
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,800
for the money.

102
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:57,120
What kind of plans?

103
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,400
Wingardium Leviosa.

104
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,920
To be or not to be.

105
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,920
In a galaxy far, far away.

106
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,920
You're not a time traveler.

107
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:15,040
What are you talking about?

108
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,200
Zhuo,

109
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:17,880
you really don't have money?

110
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,800
No.

111
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:29,000
Then let's just become sworn brothers.

112
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,000
Are you serious?

113
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,920
You said it yourself.

114
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,000
Yunhe, my brother.

115
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,040
Zhuo, my brother.

116
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,640
If we ever get rich,

117
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,360
- remember where we started.
- Remember where we started.

118
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,640
Cheers.

119
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,600
Alright,

120
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,480
I'll take my leave.

121
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,640
Leaving already?

122
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:02,720
Get back here.

123
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,200
I'll definitely

124
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,560
castrate him

125
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,600
and make him my servant!

126
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:13,460
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk)

127
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,600
After a long day,

128
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,120
I got nothing.

129
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,720
Li Yunhe,

130
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,960
I finally found you.

131
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,040
Mr. Xie,

132
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,920
long time no see.

133
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:28,840
I've got a way to make money.

134
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,000
Low risk,

135
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,120
high profit.

136
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,320
I wonder

137
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,640
if you are interested.

138
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,120
Low risk,

139
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,640
high profit?

140
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,600
If it's that good,

141
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,240
why don't you do it yourself?

142
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,360
Yunhe, you're a smart man.

143
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:44,960
I'll just put it straight.

144
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,720
My merchant ships

145
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,240
have imperial certification

146
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,360
and sail across the seas.

147
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,200
Your Gambiered Silk business

148
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,120
can use my help

149
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,240
to sell overseas.

150
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,160
(He's right.)

151
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,840
(Why didn't I think of that?)

152
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,840
(Imperial tribute was canceled,)

153
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,280
(but overseas markets)

154
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:01,240
(have never seen)

155
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,600
(such high-end products)

156
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,800
So, Xie,

157
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,400
what's the cost?

158
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,880
My grain stockpile

159
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,360
is rotting in the warehouse.

160
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,200
I really need your advice.

161
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,640
Do you want to sell it or what?

162
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,720
Money's not the issue anymore.

163
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,160
I just can't bear to let it rot

164
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,320
in storage.

165
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,400
Looks like you really can't wait

166
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,720
to get rid of it.

167
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,920
Please teach me.

168
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,280
I do have an idea.

169
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,760
Let's do this.

170
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,360
Take all your grain

171
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:31,120
to disaster-stricken areas

172
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,560
and distribute it for free.

173
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,440
Do you have the courage for that?

174
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,640
This is basically giving away silver

175
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,640
to the poor for nothing.

176
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,040
So,

177
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,440
what's the benefit?

178
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,000
Just do as I say.

179
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,920
And you'll figure it out soon.

180
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,040
Go.

181
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,560
Move all the grain in the warehouse

182
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,320
to the disaster areas.

183
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,280
Yes, sir.

184
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,720
Do you realize

185
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,560
how much Li Yunhe made for me

186
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:02,080
in this grain price war in Feng City?

187
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,280
That much?

188
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,160
At least

189
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,360
60 percent of the money

190
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,360
came from the Marquis House.

191
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,560
The Marquis House is really wealthy.

192
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,600
The Marquis of Zhennan
has ruled Feng City

193
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,280
long enough to become wealthy.

194
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:27,880
But his family is too wealthy.

195
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,080
I can't help wondering

196
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,920
if he's plotting rebellion.

197
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:36,320
He can't be.

198
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,560
What if

199
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,880
the Marquis of Zhennan

200
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,920
is recruited

201
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,120
by Prince Ning

202
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,200
and promised

203
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:44,120
a promotion to Prince of Zhennan?

204
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:01,080
Your Majesty,
an urgent report from the capital.

205
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:01,960
It sent a secret message.

206
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,160
Chancellor Sun is dead.

207
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,080
Your Majesty, should we

208
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,360
return to the capital now?

209
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,320
Not yet.

210
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,440
I'll stay in Feng City,

211
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:15,960
waiting for someone.

212
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,400
Who?

213
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,120
Chancellor Sun's granddaughter,

214
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,760
Xue Bingxiu.

215
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:25,200
Very well.

216
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,520
What a Feng City prefect.

217
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,600
No silver left in the treasury,

218
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,480
yet he still worked with Li Yunhe,

219
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,160
posting notices everywhere,

220
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,280
hiding it from the Marquis House,

221
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,760
and pushing grain prices up.

222
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,120
He simply took

223
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,400
the Marquis House for nothing!

224
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,120
My lord, I'm afraid the prefect

225
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,320
isn't the only friend

226
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,080
Li Yunhe got.

227
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,760
There must be other accomplices.

228
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,760
Exactly.

229
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,560
My lord,

230
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,480
we found that in this grain war,

231
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,080
almost all the Zhous' shops

232
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,280
were involved.

233
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,160
And they invested
a huge amount of money.

234
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,520
The Zhous, huh?

235
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,400
How dare they

236
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,960
make money from me?

237
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,360
How bodacious!

238
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,040
In this incident,

239
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,160
the Zhous

240
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:07,160
must have other accomplices.

241
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,680
After all, just the Zhou family alone

242
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:12,360
can't stand against the Marquis House.

243
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:15,080
I'm still investigating this.

244
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,320
Useless trash!

245
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,200
A secret letter from the capital.

246
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,280
My lord,

247
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,360
what does it say?

248
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,800
You have three days.

249
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,080
If you still can't find out

250
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,080
who is targeting my family,

251
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:44,680
bring your head to me!

252
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,480
Yes, yes.

253
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:53,120
Chancellor Sun is dead.

254
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,280
The three-time court veteran

255
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,760
and imperial tutor of two emperors?

256
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:02,800
And now,

257
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:05,200
his granddaughter, Xue Bingxiu,

258
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,480
has taken an imperial edict
left by the late emperor

259
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:10,000
and fled to Feng City.

260
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,600
She is now

261
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,880
hiding in Chunfeng Pavilion.

262
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:18,040
Let's go take a look.

263
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:18,920
(Xianquan Tavern)
Everyone,

264
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,800
(Xianquan Tavern)
come take a look!

265
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,600
Milk pudding is on discount today!

266
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,680
You've never tasted

267
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:25,480
anything like it!

268
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:26,840
Buy it now,

269
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,200
and you also get a free rice cake!

270
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:28,920
Don't miss it!

271
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,080
You won't regret it!

272
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,080
Let me try it.

273
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,900
Give me one portion.

274
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,160
So yummy.

275
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:35,800
I'm buying it.

276
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,320
I must support whatever Yunhe sells.

277
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,920
- Move!
- Let me through.

278
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,000
He's using my place

279
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,120
to sell this?

280
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:43,960
Yunzhuo.

281
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,960
The milk pudding is hard to get.

282
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,360
I finally got two of them.

283
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,360
Try it now.

284
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,720
I never eat those street snacks.

285
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,560
I must support whatever Yunhe sells.

286
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:54,480
I want them all!

287
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,520
There's enough for you all!

288
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,480
Don't grab!

289
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,800
Don't push me. I came first!

290
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:58,600
Hey, stop pushing!

291
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,760
I want them all!

292
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,920
Sir, hurry!

293
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:01,880
Pack it for me!

294
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,120
Listen to me,

295
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,680
