298
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,320
Six isn't much to ask, right?

299
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,120
No, can't do it.

300
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:09,880
Two per person.

301
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:10,560
That's the rule.

302
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,080
Did you hear that?

303
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,880
Two it is.

304
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,800
Make way, come on!

305
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,280
With a great reputation,

306
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:19,280
