307
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,920
What a waste of talent.

308
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,400
I won't allow you

309
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:24,000
to insult such a great product.

310
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,120
This is really good.

311
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,120
Try it.

312
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:28,080
I won't eat it.

313
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,680
Try it.

314
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:30,320
Come on, just try.

315
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,440
It's really good. Come on.

316
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:31,960
Try it.

317
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,360
Try it.

318
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,800
Try it.

319
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,800
