320
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,480
(I'm the Emperor.)

321
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,120
(No one threatens me.)

322
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,160
(If it tastes bad...)

323
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,400
It's good, right?

324
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,360
But with your personality,

325
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,360
