if you don't like it.

326
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:01,320
No.

327
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,480
It's good.

328
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,760
It really is good.

329
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,560
I haven't had something

330
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:07,080
