331
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,680
Wang, go line up.

332
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:11,520
Wait.

333
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:12,840
Get Zhang Tao

334
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:13,760
and more Shadow Guards

335
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:14,800
