336
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:18,280
(Xianquan Tavern)

337
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,080
(Xianquan Tavern)
Alas.

338
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,000
After a long day,

339
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,640
