340
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,240
Business is so tough.

341
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:27,200
This stuff is really good.

342
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,800
But earning 800 coins a day.

343
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:29,900
Isn't that too little?

344
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,400
What do you know?

345
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,960
So many people come to me for it.

346
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,880
When they get hungry,

347
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:36,800
won't they go eat

348
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,000
at Xianquan Tavern?

349
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,040
It's about

350
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:41,800
sparking a chain reaction of spending.

351
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:43,520
Business at Xianquan Tavern

352
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,680
