353
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,920
But only 800 coins a day,

354
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,680
plus the tavern's share,

355
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,680
is still not much.

356
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:51,080
At this rate,

357
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,580
