375
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:18,440
Tomorrow,

376
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,200
Chunfeng Pavilion
will hold the poetry competition.

377
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,400
Poetry competition?

378
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,400
They said you're good at poetry.

379
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:24,040
A lot of people

380
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:25,480
