391
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:45,080
Miss Zhao is so kind and beautiful.

392
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:46,400
It's just poetry.

393
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,600
I love it!

394
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:55,140
